description:
Understand the scope of the project. 
1.- Participate in the kick-off meeting in our Discord (DTag voice Channel). one hour meeting with the Guardians to understand the vision of the Project. There is going to be 3 meetings options: Monday 13, 19:00 UTC; Wednesday 15, 3:00 UTC; and Friday 17, 15:00 UTC.
2.- Provide valuable written feedback through our discord #dtag-dao channel.
3.- Share your profile name to identify you.
name: Kick-off Meeting
